    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2004-07-09</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2004-08-04T20:49:28Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Directs the Administrator of the Federal Aviation Administration to issue an order requiring: (1) the installation of secondary cockpit barriers preventing access to the flight deck of commercial aircraft; and (2) that such secondary barriers remain locked while the aircraft is in flight and the cockpit door separating the flight deck and the passenger area is open.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>To direct the Administrator of the Federal Aviation Administration to issue an order regarding secondary cockpit barriers.</title>
